main event: On 25 September, a Ground-Radar Officer reported one object moving westward at an estimated speed of 1000 mph, which maneuvered at high speed and disappeared from radar with no visual confirmation.
interesting points: The object was detected on radar for 2 minutes before disappearing., The course of the object was general westward., The object was associated with a speed estimate of 1000 mph., There was no visual observation confirming the radar detection., No further investigation was possible as stated in the report.
